The core package defines the lowest level TEAL interfaces and a few base level classes that most of the TEALFramework system classes will implement or be derived from.

Package teal.core Description

The core package defines the lowest level TEAL interfaces and a few base level classes that most of the TEALFramework system classes will implement or be derived from. It will not require any dependencies on any classes or interfaces defined elsewhere within the TEALFramework system.
